{"tid":2320723,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港廁所協會：麗晶花園與淘大花園喉管設計相似","createTime":"2020-12-11T04:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T10:19:59.000Z","uid":20933,"like":133,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"3b128092774310d3aed543da3708c881637016bb","tid":2320723,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:27:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】香港廁所協會副主席熊志權指，麗晶花園與淘大花園設計相似，均以單管式喉管排水，亦有機會忽略地台去水位隔氣問題。<br />\n<br />\n熊志權：「地台去水是很大的隱患，當年淘大花園亦是因為地台去水出現問題，這些器皿都有隔氣，以隔離臭氣。現時很少人用倒水去洗地，地台去水亦駁到去總糞管。如果日久大家都不留意，很多都不留意，這個地台去水出現問題，地台去水日子久便會乾，乾了之後污穢臭氣經總糞管在這裏走入來。」"},{"pid":"26e43d0aa0179a7cd9affe5b25c1300c885646e6","tid":2320723,"uid":20933,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:27:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=416179\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416179&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqXQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=40bfc01f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416179&h=b64ff04a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=416179</a>"},{"pid":"1ebe0f4b33aad351f0056edb972c4d2e6e6af7c2","tid":2320723,"uid":201604,"like":365,"dislike":3,"score":362,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:28:06.000Z","msg":"咩協會黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c290085e5fbeb1f91151d24b4dd83eeb037c04b","tid":2320723,"uid":7147,"like":330,"dislike":4,"score":326,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:28:26.000Z","msg":"原來有d咁既協會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec4c8bcca9ae2ee05d7fbdcf5c1eddfcef4e150","tid":2320723,"uid":8014,"like":106,"dislike":5,"score":101,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:28:29.000Z","msg":"廁所師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"